    { "id":"c-hkd-file-format","text":"HKD File Structure (.hkd) sample with hkd version / id / title / type / entities / relations / evidence / insights / metadata","status":"PARTIAL","blockedReason":"43 real .hkd files exist on disk under hkd/ — every one conforming to packages/visual-hkd-runtime/src/types.ts#VisualHKD. The board's sample fields (entities, relations, evidence) match the VisualHKD shape (nodes, edges, claims, evidence). Real format, but no compiler/validator/registry CLI exists.","sourceImage":"user-provided/2026-05-28/hkd-runtime-board.png","sourceSectionId":"sec-file-structure","confidence":0.95 },
    { "id":"c-9-entity-types","text":"9 HKD Entity Types: Concept / Entity / Person / Event / Location / Asset / Document / Observation / Evidence","status":"PARTIAL","blockedReason":"VisualHKD's HKDNode has a `kind: string` field — entity types are user-defined. The 9 named types are a sensible taxonomy but not encoded in the type system.","sourceImage":"user-provided/2026-05-28/hkd-runtime-board.png","sourceSectionId":"sec-entity-types","confidence":0.88 },
    { "id":"c-9-relation-types","text":"9 HKD Relation Types: IS_A / PART_OF / CAUSES / DEPENDS_ON / RELATED_TO / CREATED_BY / USES / SUPPORTS / CONTRADICTS","status":"PARTIAL","blockedReason":"VisualHKD's HKDEdge has a `relation: string` field — relations are user-defined. Standard semantic-web taxonomy named on board.","sourceImage":"user-provided/2026-05-28/hkd-runtime-board.png","sourceSectionId":"sec-relation-types","confidence":0.88 },
